title: Robert Palmer - Live At The Royal Albert Hall [1992]
description:
Robert Palmer - Live At The Royal Albert Hall [1992] performing Jazz Standards

While the album Ridin' High wasn't a huge commercial success it did see Robert perform two shows at London's Royal Albert Hall with a 40-piece orchestra. Here you can listen to around 46 minutes of one of those shows from a good quality recording, Lame encoded @ 192 joint stereo.
